      <section eId="sec_1355">
        <num>1355</num>
        <heading>Food service safety and sanitation training</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_1355__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>establishing\nfood service safety and sanitation training programs and providing\nstandards therefor or</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_1355__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>providing for the approval of such programs to\nbe administered by local health officials or private parties in\naccordance with such rules and regulations.\n  2. Such regulations shall include a provision permitting private\ncitizens working in establishments subject to the jurisdiction of the\ncommissioner pursuant to this title to attend such training program.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
